# Icon Processing

- Asset names/sizes come from SPEC §2 / `matrix.ts` — do not rename ad hoc.
- Use Sharp for decode, pad, resize; preserve alpha when background is `transparent`.
- Padding is % of shorter side (icons) or canvas (OG); content uses `fit: 'contain'`.
- `favicon.ico` must include 16, 32, and 48 px layers.
- Include `favicon.svg` only when the source upload is SVG.
- Package via archiver ZIP stream; no persistent temp icon files.
- OG target is exactly 1200×630 PNG (`og-image.png`).
